title: A slight change to my collection a few 206s ft
author: T206Fan

posts.post_title: A slight change to my collection a few 206s ft
posts.post_content:
I decided over the weekend that 206 portrait cards don't really grab me like the in action shots do and since 3 of the big 4 are portraits I will most likely never own them so that being said I'm putting up ft my small amount of portraits I have acquired. Looking for comparable cards in return. Sgc graded 50 or better only...
